presetNotes:
Blood reaver does a large amount of damaged throughout the fight and you shouldn't need to use scrolls

Mahj aura is bis, however vampyrism and aegis are fine alternatives for easier kills

Camp soulsplit and ideally use splitsoul
when youre comfortable staying alive
You can flick to necro pray as well on big hits to save some hp

Can make 1-2 rune pouches to save inventory space for more food but shouldnt be necessaru with practice

Manual inputs are quite important on necromancy but you can revo the 3 "basics" (basic, soul sap, and touch of death)
